# ===========================================
# Notes for External Supabase Migration:
# ===========================================
# 1. Create a new Supabase project at https://supabase.com
# 2. Copy the Project URL and anon/public key from Settings > API
# 3. Run the database migration SQL script
# 4. Deploy all 15 edge functions with required secrets:
#    - SUPABASE_URL, SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY
#    - CASHFREE_APP_ID, CASHFREE_SECRET_KEY, CASHFREE_ENVIRONMENT
#    - SMTP_HOST, SMTP_PORT, SMTP_USER, SMTP_PASSWORD, SMTP_FROM_EMAIL
#    - LOVABLE_API_KEY
# 5. Create storage buckets: question-uploads, proctoring-snapshots, 
#    student-uploads, question-images
# 6. Update this .env file with external project values
# 7. Restart the development server
